query:
SELECT p.productId, p.name, GROUP_CONCAT(c.name SEPARATOR ', ') as categories
FROM products p
JOIN product_categories pc ON p.id = pc.productId
JOIN categories c ON pc.categoryId = c.id
WHERE p.productId LIKE 'PHEN-ZB-%'
GROUP BY p.id, p.productId, p.name
LIMIT 5
